THOROUGH time-varying AR on the seasonal+backfill winner -- simple-round
validation seasons (1, 2) only, natural-scale WIS
runtime: 102.3s

Base model (unchanged): pooled seasonal climatology + per-(location,delay) backfill correction + per-location AR(6). Reference points:
  seasoncombo combo 1 core (season+AR6+backfill)  = 0.2781 (sd 0.3341)  [tuned without any time variation]
  seasoncombo combo 2 tvar (season+discounted AR, NO backfill) best = 0.2866 (discount=1.0, i.e. static was still best there too)
  local static-core sanity rerun (this script)    = 0.2781 (sd 0.3341)

